msgstr "Balance de %1"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3153
msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device. It scales only what this widget plays; the per-device volume in the system's audio settings is a separate, untouched layer — which is why those numbers differ from these sliders."
msgstr "La parte de este altavoz en el volumen: el balance sigue cada movimiento del control maestro y se recuerda para el dispositivo. Solo afecta a lo que reproduce este widget; el volumen por dispositivo en los ajustes de sonido del sistema es una capa aparte e intacta — por eso esos números difieren de estos deslizadores."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3170
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the left channel"
msgid "L"
msgstr "L"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3171
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the right channel"
msgid "R"
msgstr "R"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3172
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays a mono mix"
