msgstr "La ruta de un altavoz estaba atascada %1 ms — se vació, comprobando una vez más."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:662
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:682
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:710
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:715
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:722
